    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document clarifies an ambiguity in the Network Service Header (NSH) specification related to the handling of O bit. In particular, this document clarifies the meaning of "OAM packet".&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document updates RFC 8300.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
